Former Scandal! actress Sivenathi Mabuya finally tied the knot to her long-time boyfriend Aphiwe Bukani during a traditional ceremony in East London, Eastern Cape at the weekend. Sivenathi revealed several months ago that lobola negotiations had taken place and that she had agreed to start a new journey as the wife of Bukani. Her on-screen mother Lusanda Mbane, who shared the pictures of what the traditional ceremony looked like, shared on social media how honored she was to be the MC. “I just can’t believe how my baby has grown, it was my absolute pleasure and an honour to be on mic duty,” wrote Mbane.    Also Read: Sivenathi Mabuya gets married: YES! A thousand times more For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.